''Lepidochelys olivacea }} 'Ridley sea turtles' (Lepidochelys) are a genus of sea turtles comprising two species: Kemp's ridley sea turtle and the olive ridley sea turtle. Kemp's ridley sea turtles are currently on the New York and federal endangered species lists.
